        <item>
            <title>【評測】Acer Nitro GA1 電競熒幕，內置 Google TV + HDMI/USBC/DP 連接埠 + Mac 用家抵用熒幕之選</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/acer-nitro-ga1/wireless-home/desktop-pc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=acer-nitro-ga1</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/acer-nitro-ga1/wireless-home/desktop-pc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 12:29:04 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Notebook 配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[桌上電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流動電腦]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[評測]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[配件]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1291180</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Acer 早前推出的 Acer Nitro GA1 電競智能顯示器到了香港，這款顯示器特色在於內置 Google TV 作業系統，而且更同時備有 HDMI, DisplayPort 還有 USB-C 視訊支援，可説是滿足用家 3 個願望&#8211;直接連接 Mac 電腦作為屏幕、為手提電腦充電，而且也可連接 PS5、Xbox 等遊戲機，也可駁桌面電腦，直連高階顯示卡的 DisplayPort 插口。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291199" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04869-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04869-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04869.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291197" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04848-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04848-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04848.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291201" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04806-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04806-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04806.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Acer Nitro GA1 是一款專為遊戲玩家設計的顯示器，提供 27 吋，與 31.5 吋，兩種尺寸選擇，今次我們就測試 27 吋型號。螢幕解析度為 2560 × 1440（1440p），並具備 180Hz 更新率，為遊戲提供流暢的畫面顯示體驗。在連接 PS5 之後，我們可啟動 120Hz 選項，在連接 PS5 Pro 之後，測試玩遊戲《Marvel Spider-Man 2》享受超高流暢度，在城市中自由跳躍比很多電視機還要爽快。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291196" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04851-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04851-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04851.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲一條 USB-C 線就可將 Mac 電腦影像輸出到這部熒幕，另熒幕內置有喇叭，可播放電腦聲音</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291195" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04854-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04854-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04854.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291191" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04799-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04799-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04799.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲熒幕內置的多款模式，可迎合電腦、遊戲、影片播放的需要，提供更強色彩表現或 HDR 表現</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291192" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04800-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04800-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04800.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲熒幕提供 AMD FreeSync 支援，在玩遊戲時大幅減低畫面「撕裂」現象</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291198" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04849-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04849-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04849.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291193" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04801-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04801-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04801.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲支援 PS5 的 120Hz 輸出</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291194" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04861-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04861-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04861.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在遊玩《Marvel&#8217;s Spider-Man 2》等支援 120Hz 模式的遊戲時，可獲得更為暢快的遊戲體驗，當然駁 PS5 Pro 就更好</p><p>外觀設計方面，Nitro GA1 採用具備電競風格的支架設計，符合 Nitro 系列的美學，支援高度調整及旋轉成直立模式（Portrait Mode），適合不同的使用需求。全身白色的設計，與 PS5 等白色設計的硬件十分合襯。連接埠部分，該顯示器配備 HDMI、DisplayPort 及 USB-C，確保多樣化的連接選項，提升兼容性。USB-C 連接可駁 Mac mini、MacBook 等蘋果電腦，直接顯示畫面，並為手提電腦充電。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291183" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04784-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04784-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04784.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲操作都在機背，而且十分簡單，只有一個開關按鈕與 joystick</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291181" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04781-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04781-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04781.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲內置用家都需要的 HDMI, DisplayPort, USB-C 插口，更有 2 個 USB-A 插口給你連接滑鼠電腦</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291184" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04783-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04783-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04783.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291185" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04786-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04786-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04786.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291186" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04805-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04805-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04805.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲熒幕設計超幼邊，配合全白色機身，與 PS5 遊戲機等白色硬件十分合襯</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291187" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04797-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04797-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04797.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲你可同時連接桌面電腦、PS5 等遊戲機、Mac 電腦，在選單內自由切換</p><p>Acer Nitro GA1 本身是一個智能熒幕，它內置有 Google TV 系統。在登入 Google 帳戶後，你可在電視安裝任何 Google TV 兼容 App，系統本身就安裝了 Apple TV、Amazon Prime Video、Netflix、Disney+ 等，這些都可在毋須開電腦、遊戲機的情況下，直接利用本智能熒幕的遙控，操作睇戲、睇片。比起其他智能電視系統，Google TV 用家可自由安裝 VPN 等應用程式，應用範疇更加廣泛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291200" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04790-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04790-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04790.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲智能熒幕附隨遙控器，毋須開電腦都可播放串流影片、睇 YouTube</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291188" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04796-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04796-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04796.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291189" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04795-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04795-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04795.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Google TV 好處是讓你隨意安裝 Google TV 兼容應用程式（更可安裝部份 Android 應用程式），例如 VPN 等，應用範疇更廣</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291202" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04847-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04847-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04847.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲要特別提的是熒幕本身已有防反光設計，即使如圖找兩盞大光燈照住，反光的程度也是非常低</p><h2>結語：價值在於多種類連接</h2><p>在電腦商場逛一下你會發現千多元都有好多 27 吋熒幕選擇，之不過今次介紹的 Acer Nitro GA1（GA271U）勝在有多種輸入，把桌面電腦、手提電腦、遊戲機同一時間連接入這個熒幕都無問題。而且它更內置 Google TV 智能系統，即使不用開電腦，也可在熒幕上收看 Apple TV, Netflix, Disney+ 等串流影視 App，甚至其他 Android App（受到一定限制，並非所有 App 都能安裝／使用），例如我們常用的 VPN，都可在這個平台使用（當然常見的 Surfshark, NordVPN 等其實都有 Google TV 版）。在打機來説，這部熒幕輸出色彩較為鮮艷，具備有各種遊戲、HDR 模式，亦具有 180Hz 更新率適閤中階打機用家。如果你認為 2K 熒幕都夠用的話，Acer Nitro GA1 系列可在你的考慮之列。</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/acer-nitro-ga1/wireless-home/desktop-pc/">【評測】Acer Nitro GA1 電競熒幕，內置 Google TV + HDMI/USBC/DP 連接埠 + Mac 用家抵用熒幕之選</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
