        </item>
        <item>
            <title>TikTok 瘋傳 Apple Watch 戴落腳，用家在健身房被誤會戴電子腳鐐</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/apple-watch-ankle-trend/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-watch-ankle-trend</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/apple-watch-ankle-trend/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 09:26:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[潮流手錶]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[apple watch]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1291079</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>無論你習慣將手錶佩戴在左手還是右手，相信一般人都會將手錶戴在手腕上。不過近日 TikTok 上有 KOL 帶動一股新熱潮，建議用家不要將  Apple Watch 戴在手腕上，反而推薦用家佩戴在腳踝上，表示這種佩戴方式收集到的運動數據更加準確。然而這種新作法屢屢引發誤解，甚至讓部分佩戴者被誤認為正在接受電子監管。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291120" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/anklewatchseries9v0h-425x580.jpeg" alt="" width="425" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/anklewatchseries9v0h-425x580.jpeg 425w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/anklewatchseries9v0h.jpeg 660w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 425px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/AppleWatch/comments/1d62fi7/ankle_watch_series9/">Reddit</a></p><p>《紐約時報》報道指，健身 KOL Ana Espinal 表示，由於自己手腕較纖細，感應器無法貼合皮膚，佩戴 Apple Watch 時心率監測不穩定，導致健身應用程式紀錄時常中斷。最後 Ana Espinal 嘗試將 Apple Watch 綁於腳踝後，發現問題迎刃而解。Ana Espinal 隨後在 TikTok 分享這個小技巧，引來不少用戶仿效。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291122" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/morepeoplearenowwear-580x580.jpeg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/morepeoplearenowwear-580x580.jpeg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/morepeoplearenowwear-144x144.jpeg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/morepeoplearenowwear.jpeg 640w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/AppleWatch/comments/1im7vgy/more_people_are_now_wearing_apple_watch_on_their/">Reddit</a></p><p>《紐約時報》綜合了 5 個用家選擇將 Apple Watch 戴在腳上的原因：</p><ul><li>部分用家認為自己手腕過幼，Apple Watch 感應器無法貼近皮膚；</li><li>手腕有紋身的用家認為墨水會干擾心率感應；</li><li>有人認為戴在腳踝上可以收集更準確的步數；</li><li>部分用家手部皮膚較敏感，佩戴在腳踝上較為舒適；</li><li>有些醫療專業人員不得在手腕佩戴任何東西。</li></ul><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291125" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021134235-352x580.jpg" alt="" width="352" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021134235-352x580.jpg 352w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025021134235.jpg 546w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 352px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/discover/wearing-apple-watch-on-ankle-no-ankle-strap">TikTok</a></p><p>由於腳踝佩戴智能手錶方式較罕見，不少使用者在公眾場合時常被誤解。Ana Espinal 表示，曾經試過在健身房被誤會正在佩戴電子腳鐐，她只好解釋自己只是想獲取更準確的健身數據。至於曾醉酒駕駛被判處佩戴電子腳鐐的演員 Jason Rogers 則無法接受這股潮流。他直言：「經歷兩年電子腳鐐後，絕對不可能再戴任何東西在腳踝上！」</p><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2025/02/08/style/apple-watch-ankles.html">New York Times</a>、<a href="https://techcrunch.com/2025/02/10/tiktok-influencers-are-wearing-apple-watches-on-their-ankles/">Tech Cruch</a>、<a href="https://www.macrumors.com/2025/02/10/wearing-apple-watch-on-ankle/">Mac Rumors</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/11/apple-watch-ankle-trend/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
