            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日 LG 邀請了小編出席 2025 年第一季度產品巡禮，席間展示了全球首款透明 OLED 電視 LG SIGNATURE OLED T，LG 第二代 Styler 、PuriCare AeroBooster 和 PuriCare AeroFurniture 夜幕黑版本，實在令人目不暇接。現在就讓小編和大家一起看看這些新家電！</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291111" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04823-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04823-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04823.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291112" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04826-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04826-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04826.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291113" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04828-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04828-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04828.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>LG SIGNATURE OLED T 無界視覺體驗</h2><p>LG SIGNATURE OLED T 是 LG 今年首季度創新重點產品。LG SIGNATURE OLED T 是全球首款 77 吋透明 OLED 電視，採用真正 4K 無線顯示技術，突破現有電視技術框架，重新定義家居娛樂體驗。用戶可在「透明」與「非透明」顯示模式間自由切換，確保電視既能播放影像，也能融入空間設計，提升視覺美感。</p><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="LG Signature OLED T，全球首款透明 OLED 電視機" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1055456027?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script>▲由「非透明模式」轉換至「透明模式」</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/17fff3b35bdb459e9bf0-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/17fff3b35bdb459e9bf0-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/17fff3b35bdb459e9bf0.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲設定為透明顯示模式時，可以看穿電視背面</p><div></div><div></div><div style="padding: 177.78% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="0bde5c47-4e06-42c5-8f04-14ce0aa47ee1" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1055461878?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script>▲非透明顯示模式</p><p>LG SIGNATURE OLED T 電視通過 Zero Connect Box 無線傳輸技術運作，擺脫傳統有線連接的束縛，減少雜亂線材影響空間整潔感。此款創新的電視採用 LG α11 AI 處理器，能夠提供卓越色彩、對比度，並提升音效表現。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291107" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04838-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04838-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04838-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在關掉電視後，開啟 BAR MODE 畫面下方顯示天氣、財經、體育資訊，而電視上方保持透明</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291108" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04837-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04837-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04837.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲放大資訊</p><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291110" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04833-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04833-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04833.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><div><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291109" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04834-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04834-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04834.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲可設定關閉電視時顯示名畫或用戶指定的圖片，令空間變得更有藝術感</p><div style="padding: 75% 0 0 0; position: relative;"><iframe style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;" title="8b1c21be-7075-461e-8b35-d143f937403a" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/1055458370?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479" frameborder="0"></iframe></div><p><script src="https://player.vimeo.com/api/player.js"></script></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291114" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04807-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04807-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04807.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲電視背面</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291115" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04814-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04814-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04814.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲電視背面微距觀看</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291116" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04816-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04816-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc04816.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲無線盒子，以無線方式傳輸訊號到電視</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291065" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/8bd931cf54964ebb9a49-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/8bd931cf54964ebb9a49-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/8bd931cf54964ebb9a49.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291066" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1aa5b4c8e9343079438-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1aa5b4c8e9343079438-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1aa5b4c8e9343079438.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291067" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1165edb38c449bf9d1d-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1165edb38c449bf9d1d-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/d1165edb38c449bf9d1d.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p>LG SIGNATURE OLED T 可以設定為 T-Object 模式（常開顯示功能）以將熒幕設定為數碼畫布，另外亦設有 T-Bar 優雅訊息列，能夠增加空間氣氛，讓 LG SIGNATURE OLED T 可融入日常生活場景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/lgsignatureoledt2-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/lgsignatureoledt2-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/lgsignatureoledt2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2dd23ce8878a4b788f48-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2dd23ce8878a4b788f48-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2dd23ce8878a4b788f48.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291064" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/69061e3c997944579e1f-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/69061e3c997944579e1f-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/69061e3c997944579e1f.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><h2>LG 第二代 Styler 新增高壓蒸氣掛熨機</h2><p>LG 第二代 Styler 採用升級版高壓蒸氣技術，結合作雙重蒸氣衣物護理技術及 AI 智能偵測技術，可根據衣物重量、長度自動推薦最佳護理模式。</p><p>LG 第二代 Styler 透過天然蒸汽 99.9% 抗菌功能去除異味與細菌。可於 20 分鐘，內完成衣物整理。此外第二代 Styler 設有「智慧搖擺衣架」，透過 6 大擺動技術（抖動、擺動、甩動、飄動、搖動、整平）模擬拍打與擺動動作，更容易去除灰塵與摺痕，提升護理效果。Styler 內置高壓蒸氣掛熨機，具有 3 段式高壓蒸氣，能夠迅速撫平衣服皺摺。確保日常使用更便捷。適合繁忙都市人或對高端服飾有精緻護理需求的用戶。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1291056" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9c830c1456dd49c29336-435x580.jpeg" alt="" width="435" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9c830c1456dd49c29336-435x580.jpeg 435w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/9c830c1456dd49c29336.jpeg 675w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 435px" /></p><br /><b>
